dct_title_s: Stanford's map of China and Japan with the adjacents parts of the Russian Rebubcs., India, Burma &c
dct_alternative_sm: Map of China and Japan with the adjacents parts of the Russian Rebubcs., India, Burma &c
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights, shading and hachures.
Shows existing and projected railways, submarine telegraph cables, treaty ports -cantons, ports opened to trade -Liaoyang.
At right bottom corner: Stanfords Geographical Establishment, London.
